snippet.textDisplay:
🇬🇧PLEASE READ🇬🇧

1) Containment of this virus is not possible anymore; we had a chance a month ago and we did nothing
2) This virus is not the flu! We know a lot about the genetic make up of influenza and nothing about this coronavirus. The R0 factor of the coronavirus is around 6-8 by researchers estimates, flu is about 2-3x less than this.
3) There is a 5-15% chance that serious complications can arise from catching the virus (pneumonia for instance) which may require intensive care. There are not enough ICU units to provide care for the predicted number of infected in the next month.
4) the death rate is low for younger people, however it is still much higher than the flu.

I could go on. The media and government have been downplaying the situation. The NHS is not testing enough people and I suspect the cases in the UK are 10 fold higher than reported.

Stay safe and look after yourself
